channel.title: Data collection
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape,
I have some data I need in order to finish a project I'm working on, I just want to make sure it will be compatible to the majority of people.
I need you to post your ip configs! The data I really need is: [code] Operating System: --IP portion output-- [/code] For example, [code] Operating System: Windows 7 IPv4 Address. . . . . . . . . . . : 192.168.1.100 Subnet Mask . . . . . . . . . . . : 255.255.255.0 Default Gateway . . . . . . . . . : 192.168.1.1 [/code] [b]Thanks everyone for the help, reyx7's post was all the data I needed[br]No more needed.[/b]
